Renowned Pretoria organist Eddie Davey Port Elizabeth s Feather Market Organ Society invites all music lovers to a lunch-hour recital on Thursday. Renowned Pretoria organist Eddie Davey, on the grand organ, will deliver a 55-minute programme of large, majestic works such as Toccata by Dubois, Cesar Franck s Final and the well-known Grand March from Aida by Verdi. Davey will also play more relaxed works such as the lovely Pri re Notre Dame by L on Bo llmann. Admission is R35, and R30 for pensioners. Entrance is free for pupils and students. The recital starts at 1pm. For further information contact Albert Troskie on 082-726-9595. Related Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share